                    <div className="bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded-lg p-3 text-xs text-red-800">
                      <strong>⚠️ No age relaxation</strong> for any category — OBC, SC, ST, EWS, or PwBD. Age limit is strict for all.
                    </div>
